Echo with security, economy

For one, the CAA-NRC discussion appears to have given another leg-up to the â€œnational securityâ€ argument which flared so prominently in the wake of Pulwama and Balakot in the BJPâ€™s campaign and mobilisation ahead of the Lok Sabha polls in 2019, and which powered its renewed majority. Except that, this time, there is a crucial difference.

