â€œIf there can be certificates for moolvasis, why not for citizenship?â€ asks Madhusudan Mahto in Mantand. â€œIf you come and earn and want to settle down here, what happens to the economy? Prices are rising. We also have to look at the future of our childrenâ€, says Ganesh Kumar Verma.

